nd Coconuts to unlock the Beach and Jungle areas.\n\n* Get a High Score in each area.\n\n* Stand or Sit to play. No walking or turning required.", "short_description": "Help Jake and Jade to collect bananas and coconuts."}]}, "developer_name": "Star Gaming Network", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "http://sgngames.com/privacypolicy.php", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "http://sgngames.com/termsofservice.php", "publisher_name": "Star Gaming Network", "support_website_url": "https://sgngames.com/contactus.php", "website_url": "http://vr.sgngames.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": null, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["ARCADE"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": null, "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["GEAR_VR_CONTROLLER"], "supported_player_modes": [], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "1064943334067462"}, "review_messages": ["Hello,\n \nCongratulations! Your submission is ready to publish in the Oculus Store.\n \nYour app will be released on 3/26/2019 @10AM PST for $1.99 under the Games section of the mobile store. Let us know if you would like a different date otherwise we will proceed with launch. Please review all binaries in the STORE channel to make sure the proper supported devices are listed.  Please do not update your online services (such as your back-end servers) during your launch week.\n \nOnce your submission is published, you can access analytics here: (https://developer.oculus.com/apps/).\n \nThanks,\n \nThe Oculus Store Team\n", ""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031594_415720372537027_1981416336613441536_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e